        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're a Volosian, a deep-jungle pahtra of the southern Pulonis coasts who permanently bonded with a specially bred symbiotic ooze called a hymothoa. Your body secretes a slime that protects your coat, keeping it slippery and shiny.</p>\n<p>You gain resistance to acid damage equal to half your level (minimum 1), and a +2 circumstance bonus to Reflex saves to avoid being Engulfed by creatures and to checks to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Escape] after being Engulfed.</p>"
